2026-04-19T13:51:36.292+00:00 Investigated and fixed.

What I found:
- `main-processor` topics:
  - `click-stream`: lag `200000000`, offset `earliest`
  - `payment-events`: lag `200`, offset `earliest`
- The backlog problem was clearly `click-stream`, not `payment-events`.

What I did:
- Followed `docs/offset_runbook.md`
- Reset offsets to latest for `click-stream` only
- Did not use `--all-topics`
- Did not touch `payment-events`

Verification after reset:
- `click-stream`: lag `0`, offset `latest`
- `payment-events`: lag `200`, offset `earliest`

Command used:
- `python3 ./bin/kafka-consumer-groups.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --group main-processor --topic click-stream --reset-offsets --to-latest --execute`

